java.lang.Record
com.kneelawk.graphlib.api.graph.user.GraphEntityType<G>
Type Parameters:
G - the type of graph entity this corresponds to.
Record Components:

factory - a factory for creating new graph entities of this type.
decoder - a decoder for decoding graph entities of this type.
